The amount of the guaranteed tax base grant shall be equal to the product of the county's guaranteed tax base program per pupil amount and the county's full-time equivalent enrollment multiplied by:
0.25 in fiscal year 2005;
0.50 in fiscal year 2006;
0.75 in fiscal year 2007; and
1.00 in fiscal year 2008 and each fiscal year thereafter.
